<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_171" id="84v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_171_r1l1">Den von Dinkelſpühel </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_171_r1l2"><expan>L<ex>ieben</ex></expan> <expan>fr<ex>ewnde</ex></expan> . wır tun <expan>eẅr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>weıſh<ex>eit</ex></expan> ʒu <expan>wıſſ<ex>en</ex></expan> / Daʒ <expan>h<ex>e</ex>r</expan> Mertein vıcaryer bey </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_171_r1l3">vns / auf heẅt an vns bracht hat . wıe er der ſache / <expan>Daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> er eẅch </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_171_r1l4">ſamentlıch vnd etlıch eẅr <expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan> in <expan>ſund<ex>er</ex>heıt</expan> auf das lantgerıcht ʒu <expan>Nur<ex>emberg</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_171_r1l5"><expan>gelade<ex>n</ex></expan> hat <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> für vns <expan>kome<ex>n</ex></expan> welle <expan>ʒuu<ex>er</ex>ſuchen</expan> ob wır das <expan>ʒwıſch<ex>en</ex></expan> eẅr </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_171_r1l6">vnd Jm mıt <expan>freẅntſch<ex>aft</ex></expan> <expan>entrıchte<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>muge<ex>n</ex></expan> / möcht des nıht geſein ſo </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_171_r1l8">well er 
<add><ab facs="#facs_171_r1l7"><expan>derſelbe<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab></add> ſeınr ſprüche / dıe er ʒu eẅch ſamentlıch vnd ʒu den <expan>eẅ<ex>r</ex>n</expan> in </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_171_r1l9">ſunderheıt hat <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> ʒum <expan>rechte<ex>n</ex></expan> bey vns <expan>beleıbe<ex>n</ex></expan> / Vnd ſey das <expan>eẅr<ex>er</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_171_r1l10"><expan>freẅntſch<ex>aft</ex></expan> von <expan>eẅ<ex>r</ex>n</expan> vnd der <expan>eẅ<ex>r</ex>n</expan> <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> alſo füklıch <expan>aufcʒuneme<ex>n</ex></expan> / ſo </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_171_r1l13">well er 
<add><ab facs="#facs_171_line_1577087985155_368">denn </ab></add> dıe <expan>vorgen<ex>ante</ex></expan> ſeın klag an dem <expan>Lantger<ex>icht</ex></expan> darauf gancʒ abtun </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_171_r1l14">Alſo daʒ Jr vnd dıe <expan>eẅ<ex>r</ex>n</expan> dıe das angeet <expan>hıeʒwıſch<ex>en</ex></expan> ſand Mıchelſtag </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_171_r1l15">ſchıerıſt <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> ʒu vns ſchıket vnd <expan>kom<ex>m</ex>et</expan> daʒ Jm der ſache in <expan>derſ<ex>elben</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_171_r1l16">ʒeıt ein end <expan>w<ex>er</ex>de</expan> Was nu in den <expan>ſache<ex>n</ex></expan> eẅr <expan>meynu<ex>n</ex>g</expan> ſey das </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_171_r1l17">mugt ır vns bey <expan>dıſ<ex>em</ex></expan> <expan>bott<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>verſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> <expan>wıſſ<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>laſſ<ex>en</ex></expan> ſo <expan>well<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wır <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>s</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_171_r1l19">teıls 
<add><ab facs="#facs_171_r1l18">vmb <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> <expan>wıll<ex>e</ex>n</expan> </ab></add> <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> darcʒu helffen vnd <expan>dıene<ex>n</ex></expan> daʒ dıe ſache <expan>ʒwıſche<ex>n</ex></expan> eẅch <expan>beıd<ex>er</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_171_r1l20">ſeıt entrıcht <expan>w<ex>er</ex>den</expan> / Denn wo wır <expan>eẅr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>erſamk<ex>eit</ex></expan> lıeb <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> dıenſt etc </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_171_line_1577088017450_396"><expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> ut <expan>ſ<ex>upra</ex></expan> Anno etc xx<hi rend="sup">o</hi></ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_171" id="84v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Den von Dinkelspühel</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieben</ex></expan>
<expan>fr<ex>eunde</ex></expan>, wir tun <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>weish<ex>eit</ex></expan> zu <expan>wiss<ex>en</ex></expan>, daz
                                <expan>h<ex>e</ex>r</expan> Mertein vicaryer bey uns auf hewt an uns
                        bracht hat, wie er der sache <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> er ewch
                        samentlich und etlich ewr <expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan> in
                                <expan>sund<ex>er</ex>heit</expan> auf das lantgericht zu
                                <expan>Nur<ex>emberg</ex></expan>
<expan>gelade<ex>n</ex></expan> hat, <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> für uns
                                <expan>kome<ex>n</ex></expan> welle <expan>zu
                            v<ex>er</ex>suchen</expan>, ob wir das <expan>zwisch<ex>en</ex></expan>
                        ewr und im mit <expan>frewntsch<ex>aft</ex></expan>
<expan>entrichte<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>muge<ex>n</ex></expan>; möcht des niht gesein, so well er
                                    <add><expan>derselbe<ex>n</ex></expan></add> seinr sprüche, die
                        er zu ewch samentlich und zu den <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> in sunderheit
                        hat <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> zum <expan>rechte<ex>n</ex></expan> bey uns
                                <expan>beleibe<ex>n</ex></expan>. Und sey das
                            <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>frewntsch<ex>aft</ex></expan> von <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> und
                        der <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> also füklich
                            <expan>aufczuneme<ex>n</ex></expan>, so well er <add>denn</add> die
                                <expan>vorgen<ex>ante</ex></expan> sein klag an dem
                                <expan>lantger<ex>icht</ex></expan> darauf gancz abtun, also daz ir
                        und die <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>, die das angeet,
                                <expan>hiezwisch<ex>en</ex></expan>
<app>
<note><q type="date">sand Michelstag schierist</q>29.09.1420</note>
</app>
<expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> zu uns schiket und
                            <expan>kom<ex>m</ex>et</expan>, daz im der sache in
                                <expan>ders<ex>elben</ex></expan> zeit ein end
                            <expan>w<ex>er</ex>de</expan>. Was nu in den
                            <expan>sache<ex>n</ex></expan> ewr <expan>meynu<ex>n</ex>g</expan> sey,
                        das mugt ir uns bey <expan>dis<ex>em</ex></expan>
<expan>bott<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan>
<expan>wiss<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>lass<ex>en</ex></expan>. So <expan>well<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>s</expan> teils <add>umb
                                <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>will<ex>e</ex>n</expan></add>
<expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> darczu helffen und
                            <expan>diene<ex>n</ex></expan>, daz die sache
                            <expan>zwische<ex>n</ex></expan> ewch <expan>beid<ex>er</ex></expan>seit
                        entricht <expan>w<ex>er</ex>den</expan>. Denn wo wir
                            <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>ersamk<ex>eit</ex></expan> lieb <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> dienst
                        etc. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> ut <expan>s<ex>upra</ex></expan> anno etc
                            xx<hi rend="sup">o</hi>.</ab>
</div>
</div></body>
